    "verification_notes": "Corrections: (1) Okuvirira→Spine was WRONG — Okuvirira is a verb meaning 'to originate'. Corrected to Omugongo=Backbone/Spine. (2) Ekizinziiro (Heel alternate) REMOVED — unconfirmed, standard heel is Ekibatu. (3) Akabina (Buttock smaller ref) REMOVED — unconfirmed and duplicates existing entry. (4) Omusaayi gw'omukono→Vein corrected to clearer description. (5) Omukutu→Back kept flagged, Omugongo already covers back/spine. (6) Omukono label corrected to Hand/Arm. (7) Mu Maaso→Face clarified. (8) Entunbwe→Calf kept flagged — spelling uncertain."
